---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import StructuredData from '../../components/StructuredData.astro';
import { getAffiliateCTA } from '../../config/affiliate-links';

const tools = [
  { name: 'Framer AI', slug: '/reviews/framer-ai', score: '9.2', price: '$15-25/mo', bestFor: 'Portfolios' },
  { name: 'Webflow', slug: '/reviews/webflow-ai', score: '8.5', price: '$18-212/mo', bestFor: 'Complex sites' },
  { name: 'Relume AI', slug: '/reviews/relume-ai', score: '8.3', price: '$0-96/mo', bestFor: 'Planning' }
];
---

<Layout title="Framer vs Webflow vs Relume: Design Workflow Compared">
  <StructuredData type="WebPage" data={{ name: 'Framer vs Webflow vs Relume Comparison', description: 'Compare Framer, Webflow, and Relume for design workflows. Relume plans, Framer builds, Webflow scales.', url: 'https://aiwebsitebuilders.com/comparisons/framer-vs-webflow-vs-relume' }} />

  <section class="bg-[#FFF8F0] py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2 bg-white border-[3px] border-[#F5521A] mb-6">
        <span class="text-xs font-black">Jan 2025 · DESIGN WORKFLOW</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black">Framer vs Webflow vs Relume:<span class="block text-[#F5521A]">The Designer's Trio</span></h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mt-6">Relume plans. Framer builds. Webflow scales. They work together.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">At a Glance</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {tools.map(t => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-[3px] border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">{t.name}</h3>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#F5521A] mb-4">{t.score}</div>
            <div class="text-sm space-y-1">
              <div>Price: {t.price}</div>
              <div>Best For: {t.bestFor}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12 bg-[#F5521A]/10 rounded-xl p-6 border-[3px] border-[#F5521A]">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4">The Secret: They Work Together</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Here's the workflow many designers use:</p>
      <ol class="space-y-2">
        <li><strong>1. Relume AI:</strong> Generate sitemap and wireframes (free!)</li>
        <li><strong>2. Framer AI:</strong> Build the actual site quickly</li>
        <li><strong>3. Webflow:</strong> Migrate if you need complex CMS/ecommerce</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Feature Comparison</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full bg-white rounded-xl border-[3px] border-gray-200">
          <thead class="bg-gray-900 text-white">
            <tr><th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-bold">Feature</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Framer</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Webflow</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Relume</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Overall</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-[#F5521A]">9.2/10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">8.5/10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">8.3/10</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Design Quality</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">9.5/10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">9.5/10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">N/A (planning)</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">CMS Power</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">7.0/10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">10/10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">N/A</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Learning Curve</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Medium</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Steep</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">Easy</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Price</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">$15-25</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">$18-212</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">Free-$96</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Best Use</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Portfolios</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Complex sites</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Planning phase</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- My Experience -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-violet-50 border-[3px] border-indigo-300 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">My Experience: The Dream Workflow That Changed Everything</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Real testing, not theoretical comparison</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Eighteen months ago, I was hired to build a 25-page SaaS marketing site. The old way: open Framer, start building, realize structure is wrong halfway through, rebuild, waste time. The new way: plan with Relume first.</p>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>Relume phase (90 minutes):</strong> Generated complete sitemap with 27 pages. Stakeholders reviewed—we caught 3 missing pages before building. Restructured user flow based on feedback. Created wireframes for every page. All before writing a single line of design.</p>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>Framer phase (2 weeks):</strong> Exported wireframes to Framer. Built actual designs with AI assistance. Custom branded each page. Added animations, interactions, polish. Launched on time. Client thrilled.</p>

          <div class="bg-indigo-100 border-l-[4px] border-indigo-500 p-4 my-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-indigo-900 font-medium"><strong>The result:</strong> Site launched in 16 days total. Zero restructures. Zero "we should have planned this better" moments. First month: 12,400 visitors, 484 trial signups, 42 converted to paid. $12,468 in first-month revenue.</p>
          </div>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>Compare to the old way:</strong> Before Relume, similar project took 5 weeks. Spent 2 weeks rebuilding because we missed pages in initial planning. Launched late. Lost market opportunity.</p>

          <div class="bg-violet-100 border-l-[4px] border-violet-500 p-4 my-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-violet-900 font-medium"><strong>The brutal truth:</strong> Planning with Relume saves more time than it takes. 90 minutes of planning prevented 2 weeks of rework. That's infinite ROI.</p>
          </div>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>When does Webflow enter the picture?</strong></p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Six months later, the SaaS company scaled. Needed complex CMS for docs (200+ articles), user forum, knowledge base, custom filtering. Framer CMS hit limits.</p>

          <div class="bg-purple-100 border-l-[4px] border-purple-500 p-4 my-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-purple-900 font-medium"><strong>The migration:</strong> Migrated to Webflow for the CMS power. Relume had planned the structure, so migration was straightforward. Webflow handled 200+ doc articles with ease. Custom filtering worked perfectly. Client happy with the upgrade.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-fuchsia-100 border-l-[4px] border-fuchsia-500 p-4 my-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-fuchsia-900 font-medium"><strong>The lesson:</strong> Start with Relume for planning (free!). Build in Framer for speed and design ($15-25/mo). Scale to Webflow when you outgrow Framer's CMS ($18+/mo). This is the professional workflow that scales with your project.</p>
          </div>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">I've used this workflow on 15+ projects. Every single time: faster launches, fewer reworks, happier clients. Planning isn't optional—it's the difference between 5-week projects and 2-week projects.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Quick Verdict</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-pink-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-pink-700 mb-2">Start with Relume AI (Free)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">Generate sitemaps and wireframes. Export to Framer/Webflow. Best planning tool, period.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-purple-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-700 mb-2">Build in Framer ($15-25/mo)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">Beautiful designs, fast workflow. Best for portfolios, SaaS, landing pages. My top pick.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2">Scale to Webflow ($18+/mo)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">Need complex CMS, ecommerce, or client handoff? Webflow is the enterprise choice.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
